Feature: Update existing Product

Scenario: Successfully update an existing product
Given a product with id "54" exists
When I send a PUT request to "/product/54" with:
|   Iphone 13   |
| 128gb, Green  |
|     44990     |
Then the response status should be 200

Scenario: Update a product that does not exist
When I send a PUT request to "/product/9999" with:
|  Iphone 14  |
|256gb, black |
|   69999     |
Then the response status should be 404

Scenario: Update with invalid data
When I send a PUT request to "/product/56" with:
|           |
|1tb, Silver|
|  -499999  |
Then the response status should be 404